---
// Programming journey section with story and Notepad++ anecdote.
---

<div>
  <h2 class="text-ui-text text-3xl font-geist font-bold mb-2">My Programming Journey</h2>
  <p class="text-ui-text-muted text-sm font-geist mb-8">
    How a curiosity for Minecraft servers turned into a lifelong passion for software.
  </p>

  <div class="bg-ui-front border border-ui-border rounded-2xl p-6 md:p-8 shadow-3ui transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-1 hover:border-ui-primary">
    <p class="text-ui-text-muted text-sm leading-relaxed font-geist mb-5">
      It all started when I was 14 or 15, tinkering with Minecraft servers. I was never really into the
      game itself — what fascinated me was writing plugin configurations and seeing everything come to
      life. That curiosity stuck with me. When I got to university and chose Systems Engineering, I
      took programming seriously for the first time, and I fell in love with the craft of building
      software. From configuring servers to engineering full-stack applications, every step has been
      about turning ideas into something real.
    </p>

    <!-- Notepad++ callout -->
    <div class="relative overflow-hidden rounded-xl border border-ui-primary/20 bg-ui-primary/5 p-5 transition-all duration-300 hover:bg-ui-primary/10">
      <div class="absolute top-0 left-0 w-1 h-full bg-ui-primary rounded-r"></div>
      <div class="flex items-start gap-3 pl-3">
        <div class="shrink-0 mt-0.5">
          <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-ui-primary" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <div>
          <p class="text-sm font-geist font-semibold text-ui-text mb-1">Fun Fact</p>
          <p class="text-sm text-ui-text-muted font-geist leading-relaxed">
            One of the craziest things? A piece of code I wrote is now part of Notepad++ — my first
            contribution to a large open-source project.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
